<HEADLINE>
<P>
BEIJING EXECUTES 3 SLAYERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BEIJING 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Three murderers have been executed in Beijing as part of a crackdown on crime 
to "ensure a safe Asian Games," an official newspaper said Friday. The games 
are to start in September. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA070890-0044 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 244184 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 8, 1990, Sunday, Bulldog Edition 
</P>
