<DOCNO> LA070890-0052 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 244204 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 8, 1990, Sunday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 5; Metro Desk 
</P>
