Men have long been addressed as Mr. whether married or single. Addressing all 
women as Miss (written Ms. but not pronounced "Mizz") is being used more and 
more often. Many women do not want to be called Mrs., and it should not make 
any more difference than when addressing men as Mr. W. POWER 
