<SECTION>
<P>
San Gabriel Valley; Part J; Page 1; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
45 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
DAY TRIP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Gamble House is the most famous Greene and Greene home in Pasadena. 
</P>
<P>
Built in 1908, its original furnishings, accessories and landscaping designs 
are intact. Gamble House is a U.S. National Historic Landmark. 4 Westmoreland 
Place. Information: (818) 793-3334. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA070890-0093 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 244311 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 8, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
