<HEADLINE>
<P>
SET YOUR VCR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Kevin Thomas 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Re-Animator Stuart Gordon's 1985 film of a 1922 H.P. Lovecraft story is a real 
throat-grabber, one of the best, funniest Grand Guignol horror pictures of the 
last decade. Jeffrey Combs stars as a medical student whose genius teeters on 
madness and who is determined to conquer brain death. (2 hours) Edited. (KCOP 
Saturday at 3 p.m.) Kevin Thomas 
</P>
</TEXT>
